Jamie Lokier wrote:
> In futex.c:
> 
> 	down_read(&current->mm->mmap_sem);
> 	get_futex_key(...) etc.
> 	queue_me(...) etc.
> 	current->flags |= PF_MMAP_SEM;             <- new
> 	ret = get_user(...);
> 	current->flags &= PF_MMAP_SEM;             <- new
> 	/* the rest */
Should the second new line be this (with the inverse)?
	current->flags &= ~PF_MMAP_SEM;
